sql:
SELECT lift_id, AVG(wait_time) AS average_wait_time, AVG(average_rating) AS average_guest_rating
FROM guest_experience
GROUP BY lift_id;

SELECT AVG(wait_time) AS average_wait_time, AVG(average_rating) AS average_guest_rating
FROM guest_experience
WHERE lift_id = 1 AND date = '2023-10-01';

SELECT COUNT(*) AS lifts_needing_repair, SUM(safety_score) AS total_safety_score
FROM lift_safety
WHERE safety_status = 'needs repair';

SELECT lift_id
FROM lift_safety
WHERE next_scheduled_maintenance < '2023-12-31';

external_knowledge:
The overall performance ranking is based on the following criteria:
- 'Excellent': safety score > 80, average guest rating > 4, and operational records count > 10;
- 'Good': safety score > 70, average guest rating > 3.5, and operational records count > 7;
- 'Average': safety score > 60, average guest rating > 3, and operational records count > 5;
- 'Needs Improvement': does not meet any of the above criteria.

"Lifts pending maintenance" refers to lifts that are currently not in operation due to maintenance issues and their maintenance status is 'pending'; 
"Recent safety inspection results" refers to the most recent inspection records, which include the inspector's name, safety status, and safety score;
"Latest guest feedback" includes the average guest rating and feedback comments.

